title: Jadakiss joins the J&J!
description:
The guys are joined by the one and only, Top 5 Dead or Alive, Jadakiss! He jumps in and tells us about his 5 favorite hiphop groups, he talks Knicks and Nets, we get a peek behind the curtain for his legendar Verzus with Dipset, and his latest legacy venture with his father & son: Kiss Cafe. ORDER UP! Plus, we break down opening night in the NBA, where the Warriors and Celtics reminded everyone (including the Lakers and Sixers) why they played in the Finals this summer. All that and more!
